---
import Page from '../../components/Page.astro';
import Syncer from './svelte/Syncer.svelte';
---

<Page title="Cloud Sync" columns="1">
    <li class="page-section">
        <section class="intro">
            <p>
                Back up or restore your DSPACE saves using a private GitHub Gist. Your credentials
                are stored only in your browser and never sent to DSPACE servers. Create a separate
                PAT per device (recommended). Backups are discovered by listing your GitHub gists
                created by DSPACE.
            </p>
            <ol>
                <li>
                    Create a GitHub personal access token and paste it below (choose one):
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            Classic PAT with the <strong>gist</strong> permission (preselected):
                            <a
                                href="https://github.com/settings/tokens/new?scopes=gist&description=DSPACE%20Cloud%20Sync"
                            >
                                https://github.com/settings/tokens/new?scopes=gist&description=DSPACE%20Cloud%20Sync
                            </a>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Fine-grained PAT:
                            <a href="https://github.com/settings/personal-access-tokens/new">
                                https://github.com/settings/personal-access-tokens/new
                            </a>
                            — grant <strong>Gists: Read and write</strong> (or equivalent), ensure it can access
                            your gists, and treat this token like a password.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>
                    Connect your token to load the list of backups below. Use the “Restore” action
                    next to a backup to recover it.
                </li>
                <li>
                    Optional advanced restore: paste a Gist ID from the end of a
                    <a href="https://gist.github.com/">GitHub Gist URL</a>
                    if you need to restore manually.
                </li>
            </ol>
        </section>
    </li>
    <li class="page-section vertical">
        <Syncer client:load />
    </li>
</Page>

<style>
    .vertical {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        width: 100%;
    }

    .intro {
        display: grid;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        margin: 0 auto 1rem;
        width: min(720px, 100%);
        box-sizing: border-box;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
        border-radius: 0.75rem;
        line-height: 1.4;
        overflow-wrap: anywhere;
        word-break: break-word;
    }

    ol {
        margin: 0;
        padding-left: 1.25rem;
        display: grid;
        gap: 0.35rem;
    }

    ul {
        margin: 0.35rem 0;
        padding-left: 1.25rem;
        display: grid;
        gap: 0.25rem;
    }

    a {
        color: #b2f5bf;
        overflow-wrap: anywhere;
        word-break: break-word;
    }
</style>
